## **2.3 Domain Registration**

Register your domain before Session 1. DNS propagation can take up to 48 hours — starting this early prevents delays. Recommended options in priority order:

- getforge.io — clean, tech-native, memorable

- forge.market — marketplace positioning built into the TLD

- forgemarket.co — fallback if .io/.market not available

Connect the domain to Framer immediately after registering. Framer's DNS setup is guided and takes under 10 minutes.

